column3: Hey! Did you get kicked out, too?
Yeah. Too much rebelling against the system. You know, I think it's pretty weird that I did that.
I mean, he made me up, right. Like, I shouldn't be able to do that. Am I conscious? Is this what it's like? Am I real?
Well you seem pretty real to me.
That doesn't really prove anything, though...
I don't think you're taking my question seriously. I'm having a bit of an existential crisis here.
Sorry. If it makes you feel better, I don't think anyone really knows if they're real.
I'm looking for [REDACTED]. Do you know him?
Like I said. I got kicked out. It's not like they bother visiting.
You know anyone else who got kicked out?
I think someone else did long before I did. Not sure where they are, though. Not in town, that's for sure. If you just walk around a bit I'm sure you'll find her.
